data.description:
Check out this cozy, little 3BD, 2BA home situated on a sidewalk-lined street in Hopewell. This home was updated just a few years ago, with: a new roof, water heater, flooring, paint, countertops, and HVAC. The home boasts a beautiful, light & bright spacious eat-in kitchen, which opens up to the living room. Down the hall, you will find the bathroom, 2 bedrooms, and the primary bedroom with an ensuite bathroom. In the backyard, there is a really nice shed for storage, as well as room to cook out or just relax with friends and family. This home is centrally located, being just minutes from shops, restaurants, gas stations, and more. It is just a 6 minute drive to pick up 295. This is a great little home at a really great price. It won’t last long!!
NOTE: The dryer and icemaker are being sold in as-is condition.
